summary: Removes annoying and pointless creatures called ''Skeever'' from the game.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#6aa84f][size=5]What is This?
[/size][/color][size=3]This mod completely removes skeevers from the game. I find them annoying and pointless.[/size]
[color=#6aa84f][size=5]
How to Install?
[/size][/color][size=3]Automatically by NMM or manually dragging the esp to your data folder.[/size][/font][/center][center]
[font=Lucida Sans Unicode][size=3][/size][/font][/center]
